summary: Prince Arthas from Warcraft is back
descriptionHtml:
This is my Arthas - Deathknight save game
His abilities and Gear is similar to Arthas from Warcraft:
1: Necromantic Healing - Death coil
2: Cyromancer Aura - Unholy Aura
3: Animate Dead - The Ritual Power ( see the pics )
4: Frostmourne
5: Lich King\'s Armour
\"This kingdom shall fall and from the ashes shall arise a new order\"
Require mode :
Skyrim redone (http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/9286)
Lich King\'s collector edition ( http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/25696)
author: Jared
